::Prowl::

Prowl nods. "Do you think you can keep it safe? If you don't, you could give 
it to Iron Raptor when she returns," Prowl says, leaving out the fact that 
Iron Raptor was kidnapped and that he and Dinobot were about to go on a 
highly suicidal mission to rescue her and Tavatron.
